---
title: Quick Ginger-Teriyaki Pork Loin Noodle Stir Fry with Veggies & Coriander
description: A pork stir-fry is a takeaway classic, but we think we can do it better at home. Tender veggies, juicy pork and slurpable egg noodles come together in a snap, with a sweet and savoury teriyaki sauce and an extra punch of flavour coming from the addition of ginger paste. Grab a bowl and eat up!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
